title: Las Vegas Complete
description:
This is the complete batch for the totally awesome series Las Vegas Season 1-5.


Unfortunately Season 5 episode 3 & 5 got French subtitle(Still English sound) and I have not found any in English.


Found one torrent on the whole web and the speed was ridiculously low.
Then I remembered I had em burned on DVD(lol) LONG ago so I made a new, better and improved torrent out of fury ^^

Credit to the creators of Las Vegas and to the original rippers.


Do help seed after you are done!
